summary: Check that tree package was installed via prepare/shell
description: |
    Verify that the tree command is available after prepare/shell
    executed 'dnf -y install tree' via the bootc Containerfile build.
test: |
    # Verify tree is installed and working
    tree --version
    # Also verify the booted image shows we're running a modified image
    bootc status --booted --format humanreadable
